The '''Holy Advisor''' was the representative of the planet [[Gascon]]'s [[Akol]] religion to its monarchy. The [[Unidentified Holy Advisor|Holy Advisor]] during the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]], was a corrupt man who gained both power and wealth from the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]] prior to the death of [[Galactic Emperor/Legends|Emperor]] [[Palpatine/Legends|Palpatine]].

